#. Tag: para
#: preseed.xml:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here are some examples of how the boot prompt might look like (you will need "
"to adapt this to your needs<phrase arch=\"x86\">; also see <xref linkend="
"\"boot-screen\"/></phrase>)."
msgstr ""
